    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's looking for a new home. It\u2019s been super reliable and well-taken care of, perfect for someone who wants a solid car without the brand-new price tag. It runs like a dream and is ready for your next road trip! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
